# Cline Project Rules — UI Design Evaluator (Planner-Generator-Evaluator)

## Project Purpose

This project is a **harness** that runs a Planner → Generator → Evaluator loop to produce
React UI components that are fully compliant with the company design system.

You are acting as an autonomous frontend coding agent. Never output raw HTML or CSS
that bypasses the design system. Always use design system components and tokens.

---

## Architecture Overview

```
UIRequest
    │
    ▼
┌─────────┐
│ PLANNER │  Decomposes the request into a structured component plan.
│  Agent  │  Output: Plan (component tree, required DS components, layout, state)
└────┬────┘
     │ Plan
     ▼
┌─────────────┐
│  GENERATOR  │◄──── feedback (on retry)
│    Agent    │  Writes TSX files using DS components + tokens only.
└──────┬──────┘
       │ GeneratedCode
       ▼
┌───────────┐
│ EVALUATOR │  Static-analyzes code against design system rubric.
│  (static) │  Output: EvaluationResult (weighted score per criterion)
└─────┬─────┘
      │
      ├── score ≥ threshold ──► Return result ✓
      │
      └── score < threshold ──► Feed violations back to Generator (retry)
```

Max retries: 3 (configurable via HARNESS_MAX_ATTEMPTS env var)
Pass threshold: 0.80 weighted score (configurable via HARNESS_PASS_THRESHOLD)

---

## Design System Rules for the Generator Agent

When writing React components:

### DO
- Use design system components for all interactive and semantic elements:
  - `<Button>` instead of `<button>`
  - `<TextInput>`, `<Checkbox>`, `<Radio>` instead of `<input>`
  - `<Select>` or `<Combobox>` instead of `<select>`
  - `<Link>` instead of `<a>`
  - `<DataTable>` instead of `<table>`
  - `<Textarea>` instead of `<textarea>`
- Use design token CSS variables for all visual values:
  - Colors: `var(--color-*)` tokens only
  - Spacing: `var(--spacing-*)` tokens only
  - Typography: `var(--font-size-*)`, `var(--font-weight-*)` tokens only
  - Shadows: `var(--shadow-*)` tokens only
  - Motion: `var(--duration-*)`, `var(--easing-*)` tokens only
- Use layout primitives: `<Stack>`, `<Grid>`, `<Cluster>`, `<Sidebar>`
- Wrap component trees in `<ThemeProvider>`
- Add `prefers-reduced-motion` guards around new animations
- Ensure interactive elements are keyboard accessible (role, tabIndex, aria-*)

### DO NOT
- Hardcode hex colors, rgb(), rgba(), hsl() values
- Hardcode px/rem/em for margin, padding, gap, font-size, font-weight
- Use raw `box-shadow` without `var(--shadow-*)` tokens
- Use raw `@media (min-width: Npx)` — use DS breakpoint tokens
- Apply `style={{}}` overrides on DS components
- Inject arbitrary `className` onto DS components
- Use invalid prop values on DS components (check the component's type signature)

---

## Evaluator Scoring

The evaluator runs static analysis (no LLM) and returns a weighted score 0–1.

**Hard gates** (must pass or generation is rejected regardless of score):
- `theme_provider_scope`: component tree wrapped in `<ThemeProvider>`
- `focus_management`: no `onClick` on non-interactive elements without role/tabIndex

**Weighted criteria** (score ≥ threshold required):
| Criterion            | Weight | Threshold |
|----------------------|--------|-----------|
| color_tokens         | 0.15   | 0.70      |
| spacing_tokens       | 0.12   | 0.70      |
| typography_tokens    | 0.08   | 0.70      |
| shadow_tokens        | 0.05   | —         |
| native_override_rate | 0.15   | 0.80      |
| prop_correctness     | 0.12   | 0.80      |
| layout_primitives    | 0.08   | —         |
| axe_violations       | 0.12   | 0.70      |
| contrast_ratio       | 0.08   | 0.90      |
| motion_tokens        | 0.03   | —         |
| reduced_motion_guard | 0.02   | —         |

---

## File Structure

```
src/
├── index.ts                # CLI entry point
├── harness.ts              # PGE orchestration loop
├── types.ts                # Shared TypeScript types
├── agents/
│   ├── planner.ts          # Planner agent (Claude API)
│   ├── generator.ts        # Generator agent (Claude API)
│   └── prompts/
│       ├── planner.md      # Planner system prompt
│       └── generator.md    # Generator system prompt
├── evaluator/
│   ├── index.ts            # Evaluator runner
│   ├── rubric.ts           # Rubric definition + score assembly
│   ├── token-compliance.ts # Color, spacing, typography, shadow checks
│   ├── component-usage.ts  # Native element override, prop correctness
│   ├── accessibility.ts    # Axe violations, contrast ratio
│   ├── responsive.ts       # Breakpoint adherence, layout primitives
│   └── motion.ts           # Motion tokens, reduced-motion guard
└── config/
    ├── ds-components.ts    # Design system component map
    └── ds-tokens.ts        # Design system token registry
```

---

## Environment Variables

```
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-...         # Required
HARNESS_MAX_ATTEMPTS=3           # Default: 3
HARNESS_PASS_THRESHOLD=0.80      # Default: 0.80
HARNESS_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6  # Default: claude-sonnet-4-6
```
